flowchart TB
    Caller([Trusted local caller]) --> ToolAPI[Tool-memory API<br/>/memory/user/tools]
    ToolAPI --> Ownership[Optional signed-user ownership]
    Ownership --> Schema[Pydantic allowlists and size limits]
    Schema --> Sensitive[Sensitive-marker rejection<br/>no credentials, arguments, outputs, or resources]
    Sensitive --> Service[ToolMemoryService]

    Service --> DescriptorPath[Descriptor path]
    DescriptorPath --> Identity[Canonical server, tool, version,<br/>and schema fingerprint]
    Identity --> Deactivate[Deactivate prior descriptor<br/>when schema fingerprint changes]
    Deactivate --> Embed[Embed safe descriptor text]
    Embed --> Nomic[LM Studio Nomic]
    Nomic --> Descriptors[(tool_descriptors<br/>active flag and HNSW cosine index)]

    Service --> PreferencePath[Approved preference path]
    PreferencePath --> Preferences[(tool_preferences<br/>allowlisted keys, provenance, optional expiry)]
    Service --> OutcomePath[Sanitized outcome path]
    OutcomePath --> Outcomes[(tool_usage_outcomes<br/>category and bounded metadata)]

    Coordinator[MemoryCoordinatorAgent] -->|semantic descriptor search| Service
    Descriptors --> Service
    Preferences --> Service
    Outcomes --> Service
    Service --> Toolbox[Bounded toolbox context<br/>untrusted literal metadata]
    Toolbox --> Gemma[Gemma prompt context]

    Database[(PostgreSQL and pgvector)]
    Descriptors --> Database
    Preferences --> Database
    Outcomes --> Database

    Boundary[Current safety boundary:<br/>discovery and memory only<br/>no MCP connection, permission, or execution]
    Service -.-> Boundary

